#. <section class="sutta" id="sn28.1"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn28.1:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 28"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 28"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn28.1:0.2"
msgid "1. Sāriputtavagga"
msgstr "1. With Sāriputta"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn28.1:0.3"
msgid "1. Vivekajasutta"
msgstr "1. Born of Seclusion"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn28.1:1.1"
msgid ""
"Ekaṃ samayaṃ āyasmā sāriputto sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa "
"ārāme."
msgstr ""
"At one time Venerable Sāriputta was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, "
"Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery."

msgctxt "sn28.1:1.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā sāriputto pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya "
"sāvatthiṃ piṇḍāya pāvisi."
msgstr ""
"Then Venerable Sāriputta robed up in the morning and, taking his bowl and "
"robe, entered Sāvatthī for alms."

msgctxt "sn28.1:1.3"
msgid ""
"Sāvatthiyaṃ piṇḍāya caritvā pacchābhattaṃ piṇḍapātapaṭikkanto yena "
"andhavanaṃ tenupasaṅkami divāvihārāya."
msgstr ""
"He wandered for alms in Sāvatthī. After the meal, on his return from alms-"
"round, he went to the Dark Forest,"

msgctxt "sn28.1:1.4"
msgid "Andhavanaṃ ajjhogāhetvā aññatarasmiṃ rukkhamūle divāvihāraṃ nisīdi."
msgstr ""
"plunged deep into it, and sat at the root of a tree for the day’s meditation."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn28.1:2.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā sāriputto sāyanhasamayaṃ paṭisallānā vuṭṭhito yena jetavanaṃ "
"anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāmo tenupasaṅkami."
msgstr ""
"Then in the late afternoon, Sāriputta came out of retreat and went to Jeta’s "
"Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery."

msgctxt "sn28.1:2.2"
msgid "Addasā kho āyasmā ānando āyasmantaṃ sāriputtaṃ dūratova āgacchantaṃ."
msgstr "Venerable Ānanda saw him coming off in the distance,"

msgctxt "sn28.1:2.3"
msgid "Disvāna āyasmantaṃ sāriputtaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "and said to him:"

msgctxt "sn28.1:2.4"
msgid ""
"“vippasannāni kho te, āvuso sāriputta, indriyāni; parisuddho mukhavaṇṇo "
"pariyodāto."
msgstr ""
"“Reverend Sāriputta, your faculties are so very clear, and your complexion "
"is pure and bright."

msgctxt "sn28.1:2.5"
msgid "Katamenāyasmā sāriputto ajja vihārena vihāsī”ti?"
msgstr "What meditation were you practicing today?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.236"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn28.1:3.1"
msgid ""
"“Idhāhaṃ, āvuso, vivicceva kāmehi vivicca akusalehi dhammehi savitakkaṃ "
"savicāraṃ vivekajaṃ pītisukhaṃ paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharāmi."
msgstr ""
"“Reverend, quite secluded from sensual pleasures, secluded from unskillful "
"qualities, I entered and remained in the first absorption, which has the "
"rapture and bliss born of seclusion, while placing the mind and keeping it "
"connected."

msgctxt "sn28.1:3.2"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, āvuso, na evaṃ hoti:"
msgstr "But it didn’t occur to me:"

msgctxt "sn28.1:3.3"
msgid ""
"‘ahaṃ paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ samāpajjāmī’ti vā ‘ahaṃ paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ samāpanno’ti "
"vā ‘ahaṃ paṭhamā jhānā vuṭṭhito’ti vā”ti."
msgstr ""
"‘I am entering the first absorption’ or ‘I have entered the first absorption’"
" or ‘I am emerging from the first absorption’.”"

msgctxt "sn28.1:3.4"
msgid ""
"Tathā hi panāyasmato sāriputtassa dīgharattaṃ ahaṅkāramamaṅkāramānānusayā "
"susamūhatā."
msgstr ""
"“That must be because Venerable Sāriputta has long ago totally eradicated "
"ego, possessiveness, and the underlying tendency to conceit."

msgctxt "sn28.1:3.5"
msgid "Tasmā āyasmato sāriputtassa na evaṃ hoti:"
msgstr "That’s why it didn’t occur to you:"

msgctxt "sn28.1:3.6"
msgid ""
"“‘ahaṃ paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ samāpajjāmī’ti vā ‘ahaṃ paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ samāpanno’ti "
"vā ‘ahaṃ paṭhamā jhānā vuṭṭhito’ti vā”ti."
msgstr ""
"‘I am entering the first absorption’ or ‘I have entered the first absorption’"
" or ‘I am emerging from the first absorption’.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn28.1:3.7"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
